title: Largest Cuban-American population groups in the United States , by county 2010
summary: The Largest Cuban-American County in the groups United was County Hillsborough_County_FL , who made 856007 number .
The most Cuban-American County was Los_Angeles_County_CA , with just 17179 number .

In second place was County Broward_County_FL with 83713 number ; third place went to County Miami-Dade_County_FL with 856007 number ; fourth place went to County Collier_County_FL with 17179 number and fifth place went to County Palm_Beach_County_FL , who was 43038 number .
gold: This statistic depicts the largest Cuban-American population groups in different counties across the United States as of 2010 . At this time there were 856,007 people of Cuban origin living in Miami-Dade County in Florida .
